<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
Rules of personal pictures &amp; signature size<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
First, please keep your personal picture restricted to 130 WIDTH *max*, smaller personal pictures are always preferred.<br>
<br>
Second, don't make your personal pictures large. Keep the height small, so we don't get any useless unused space to download because your picture is larger than the height of your post. My advice is 130 also. This may change a bit, but please keep it *small*.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
How to make your huge personal picture 130 WIDTH:<br>
1) Go to &quot;My Control Center&quot;<br>
2) Go to &quot;Edit Preferences&quot;<br>
3) At personal photo, fill in (just an example):<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.mysite.com/pictures/myhead.jpg">www.mysite.com/pictures/myhead.jpg</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> WIDTH=130 HEIGHT=100<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Third, please do not use BMP and keep FLASH and animated GIF's to a minimum. FLASH and animated GIF's do not only take ages to load, they also use a lot of CPU speed, which may cause problems at some of the older computers.<br>
<br>
Fourth, please do not make people download more than 50KB. That's personal picture and signature together. <br>
